shortDescription.en: Charming chalet with stunning mountain views in Comarnic.
shortDescription.ro: Charming chalet with stunning mountain views in Comarnic.

description.en: Escape to our charming chalet in the Prahova Valley. Enjoy stunning mountain views, fresh air, and a peaceful atmosphere. Perfect for families or groups seeking a relaxing getaway near hiking trails and nature. Fully equipped kitchen, cozy fireplace, and a spacious garden await.
description.ro: Escape to our charming chalet in the Prahova Valley. Enjoy stunning mountain views, fresh air, and a peaceful atmosphere. Perfect for families or groups seeking a relaxing getaway near hiking trails and nature. Fully equipped kitchen, cozy fireplace, and a spacious garden await.
